overview: Chris Ward here, President of Raging Stallion Studios. I am really excited to announce the release of a great new fisting film entitled What's Happening Down There? It was directed by our very own award-winning director, Ben Leon. This movie is an excellent addition to our library of uncensored, controversial ass-play movies and it boasts some of the best men and finest footage we have ever filmed.
title: Fistpack 23: What's Happening Down There?
